{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/KA_SteamGIFs.gif?t=1738915124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The future of turn-based RPGs is here!</strong><br><br>Recruit loyal knights, explore a vast medieval fantasy world, and restore the kingdom of Camelot to its former glory.<br><br>War between the gods and mankind rages across Britain! Arthur, drawn to the blade Excalibur, has made a dark pact with Caliburn, the dragon trapped within the sword. Now, wielding the power of Excalibur, Arthur must lead his kingdom through an age of darkness as dangerous enemies and vile creatures threaten him at every turn.<br><br>Will you make a deal with the dragon?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/KA_SteamGIFs_2.gif?t=1738915124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25b6 Embark on an epic adventure!</strong><br><br>Ancient gods, dragons, and magic await - join King Arthur and explore a brand new medieval fantasy world. What do the ancient gods desire? What price will Arthur's blood pact with Excalibur demand? Will the kingdom of Camelot prevail? Only you can discover the answers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/KA_SteamGIFs_3.gif?t=1738915124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25b6 Battle alongside mythical heroes!</strong><br><br>Collect and power up heroes from the legend of King Arthur and take on powerful enemies. Obtain powerful elemental artifacts, swap them out as needed, and perfect your strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/KA_SteamGIFs_4.gif?t=1738915124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25b6 Turn-based combat evolved!</strong><br>With a focus on player-driven cohesive combat and hero designs to back it up, King Arthur: Legends Rise represents the next evolution of the turn-based RPG genre. Stay tuned for story updates, new game modes, and even more content coming up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/KA_SteamGIFs_5.gif?t=1738915124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25b6\u00a0Co-op Play with Clan Friends </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge periodic Clan Wars, work together with your members to destroy the enemy's Footholds and conquer their Field! You can attack a single Foothold simultaneously with up to 3 friends. Compare everyone's carefully built teams, analyze their individual strengths, and combine them to create the best strategy to take down the enemy's Field!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/250207_\ud0b9\uc544\uc11c_\uc2a4\ud300\uba54\ud0c0\ub370\uc774\ud130\uc6a9.gif?t=1738915124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The War Begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279730/24487c9cf2fca19b4a430023abcb45deeb29bf2d.jpg"},{"name":"Squire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279730/aa2ee640f5e6479b246508271bdbeeeab772a78d.jpg"},{"name":"The Scent of Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279730/0d8b22bbf3e29a2607455626cbbb02e3519b0501.jpg"